<div class=3D"math_theorem" style=3D"">
<p><strong class=3D"theorem-name">Theorem</strong><span class=3D"theoreme-t=
iret">=E2=80=94</span>Let <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i></span> and <span=
 class=3D"texhtml"><i>g</i></span> be nonzero polynomials over a field <spa=
n class=3D"texhtml"><i>K</i></span>. Write <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>g</i>=
</span> as a product of powers of distinct irreducible polynomials&nbsp;:
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle g=3D\prod _{i=3D1}^{k}p_{i}^{n_{i}}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>g</mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <munderover>
          <mo>=E2=88=8F<!-- =E2=88=8F --></mo>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>i</mi>
            <mo>=3D</mo>
            <mn>1</mn>
          </mrow>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>k</mi>
          </mrow>
        </munderover>
