n decomposition, quotients of linear polynomials by powers of quadratic pol=
ynomials may also occur.
</p><p>In the preceding theorem, one may replace "distinct irreducible poly=
nomials" by "<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pairwise_coprime" cla=
