a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Square-free_factorization" class=3D=
"mw-redirect" title=3D"Square-free factorization">square-free factorization=
</a> of <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>g</i></span>. When <span class=3D"texhtm=
l"><i>K</i></span> is the field of <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/Rational_number" title=3D"Rational number">rational numbers</a>, as it is =
typically the case in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_alg=
ebra" title=3D"Computer algebra">computer algebra</a>, this allows to repla=
ce factorization by <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polynomial_gre=
atest_common_divisor" title=3D"Polynomial greatest common divisor">greatest=
 common divisor</a> computation for computing a partial fraction decomposit=
ion.
</p>
