<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Example_2">Example 2</h3><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DPartial_fraction_d=
