<p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"m=
we-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math=
 display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"=
{\displaystyle f(x)=3D{\frac {x^{3}+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>3</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>16</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>3</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle f(x)=3D{\frac=
 {x^{3}+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/237468007296fea20672d96cb48be41a6344d62b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.338ex; width:22.455ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle f=
(x)=3D{\frac {x^{3}+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}}"></span>
</p><p>After <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polynomial_long_divis=
ion" title=3D"Polynomial long division">long division</a>, we have
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle f(x)=3D1+{\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}=3D1+{\=
frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x(x^{2}-4x+8)}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>16</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>3</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>16</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle f(x)=3D1+{\fr=
ac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}=3D1+{\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x(x^{2}-4x+8)=
}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/b081df5b412cbc14879743d2bd3dfad068003159" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.671ex; width:49.254ex; height:6.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle f=
(x)=3D1+{\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x^{3}-4x^{2}+8x}}=3D1+{\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x=
(x^{2}-4x+8)}}}"></span>
</p><p>The factor <i>x</i><sup>2</sup> =E2=88=92 4<i>x</i> + 8 is irreducib=
le over the reals, as its <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Discrimi=
nant" title=3D"Discriminant">discriminant</a> <span class=3D"texhtml">(=E2=
=88=924)<sup>2</sup> =E2=88=92 4=C3=978 =3D =E2=88=9216</span> is negative.=
 Thus the partial fraction decomposition over the reals has the shape
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle {\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x(x^{2}-4x+8)}}=3D{\frac {A}{x}}+=
{\frac {Bx+C}{x^{2}-4x+8}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>16</mn>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mi>A</mi>
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mrow>
              <mi>B</mi>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mi>C</mi>
            </mrow>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\frac {4x^{2=
}-8x+16}{x(x^{2}-4x+8)}}=3D{\frac {A}{x}}+{\frac {Bx+C}{x^{2}-4x+8}}}</anno=
tation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/b2aae914ce7dd3be7ae89a088546004fc2148c6a" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.671ex; width:36.768ex; height:6.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {=
\frac {4x^{2}-8x+16}{x(x^{2}-4x+8)}}=3D{\frac {A}{x}}+{\frac {Bx+C}{x^{2}-4=
x+8}}}"></span>
</p><p>Multiplying through by <i>x</i><sup>3</sup> =E2=88=92 4<i>x</i><sup>=
2</sup> + 8<i>x</i>, we have the polynomial identity
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle 4x^{2}-8x+16=3DA\left(x^{2}-4x+8\right)+\left(Bx+C\righ=
t)x}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mn>4</mn>
        <msup>
          <mi>x</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mn>2</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mn>8</mn>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mn>16</mn>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>A</mi>
        <mrow>
          <mo>(</mo>
          <mrow>
            <msup>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                <mn>2</mn>
              </mrow>
            </msup>
            <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
            <mn>4</mn>
            <mi>x</mi>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <mn>8</mn>
          </mrow>
          <mo>)</mo>
        </mrow>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mrow>
          <mo>(</mo>
          <mrow>
            <mi>B</mi>
            <mi>x</mi>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <mi>C</mi>
          </mrow>
          <mo>)</mo>
        </mrow>
        <mi>x</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 4x^{2}-8x+16=
=3DA\left(x^{2}-4x+8\right)+\left(Bx+C\right)x}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/09f6c7fb4883a09d7ef5f5c5e02c14f7074856a5" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -1.005ex; width:47.189ex; height:3.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle 4=
x^{2}-8x+16=3DA\left(x^{2}-4x+8\right)+\left(Bx+C\right)x}"></span>
</p><p>Taking <i>x</i> =3D 0, we see that 16 =3D 8<i>A</i>, so <i>A</i> =3D=
 2.  Comparing the <i>x</i><sup>2</sup> coefficients, we see that 4 =3D <i>=
A</i> + <i>B</i> =3D 2 + <i>B</i>, so <i>B</i> =3D 2.  Comparing linear coe=
fficients, we see that =E2=88=928 =3D =E2=88=924<i>A</i> + <i>C</i> =3D =E2=
=88=928 + <i>C</i>, so <i>C</i> =3D 0.  Altogether,
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle f(x)=3D1+2\left({\frac {1}{x}}+{\frac {x}{x^{2}-4x+8}}\=
right)}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mn>2</mn>
        <mrow>
          <mo>(</mo>
          <mrow>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <mfrac>
                <mn>1</mn>
                <mi>x</mi>
              </mfrac>
            </mrow>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <mfrac>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow>
                  <msup>
                    <mi>x</mi>
                    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                      <mn>2</mn>
                    </mrow>
                  </msup>
                  <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
                  <mn>4</mn>
                  <mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mn>8</mn>
                </mrow>
              </mfrac>
            </mrow>
          </mrow>
          <mo>)</mo>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle f(x)=3D1+2\le=
ft({\frac {1}{x}}+{\frac {x}{x^{2}-4x+8}}\right)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/f1c89a83c748ea528d9ecfefd2715a4d24111e05" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.505ex; width:34.051ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle f=
(x)=3D1+2\left({\frac {1}{x}}+{\frac {x}{x^{2}-4x+8}}\right)}"></span>
</p><p>The fraction can be completely decomposed using <a href=3D"https://e=
n.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complex_numbers" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Comple=
x numbers">complex numbers</a>. According to the <a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
pedia.org/wiki/Fundamental_theorem_of_algebra" title=3D"Fundamental theorem=
 of algebra">fundamental theorem of algebra</a> every complex polynomial of=
 degree <i>n</i> has <i>n</i> (complex) roots (some of which can be repeate=
d). The second fraction can be decomposed to:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle {\frac {x}{x^{2}-4x+8}}=3D{\frac {D}{x-(2+2i)}}+{\frac =
{E}{x-(2-2i)}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mi>x</mi>
            <mrow>
              <msup>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mn>2</mn>
                </mrow>
              </msup>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>4</mn>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>8</mn>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mi>D</mi>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mo>+</mo>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mi>i</mi>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mi>E</mi>
            <mrow>
              <mi>x</mi>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mi>i</mi>
              <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\frac {x}{x^=
{2}-4x+8}}=3D{\frac {D}{x-(2+2i)}}+{\frac {E}{x-(2-2i)}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/39ea09819761a0492735f76e6c1513a68fa78960" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -2.671ex; width:44.061ex; height:6.009ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {=
\frac {x}{x^{2}-4x+8}}=3D{\frac {D}{x-(2+2i)}}+{\frac {E}{x-(2-2i)}}}"></sp=
an>
</p><p>Multiplying through by the denominator gives:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle x=3DD(x-(2-2i))+E(x-(2+2i))}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
