(2+2i)}}+{\frac {1+i}{x-(2-2i)}}}"></span>
</p><p>One may also compute directly <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>A</i>, <i>D=
</i></span> and <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>E</i></span> with the residue me=
thod (see also example 4 below).
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Example_3">Example 3</h3><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DPartial_fraction_d=
ecomposition&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D15" title=3D"Edit section: Exa=
mple 3"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span=
></span></div>
<p>This example illustrates almost all the "tricks" we might need to use, s=
hort of consulting a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_alge=
bra_system" title=3D"Computer algebra system">computer algebra system</a>.
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle f(x)=3D{\frac {x^{9}-2x^{6}+2x^{5}-7x^{4}+13x^{3}-11x^{=
2}+12x-4}{x^{7}-3x^{6}+5x^{5}-7x^{4}+7x^{3}-5x^{2}+3x-1}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
